title: Spider-Man and Zoids (001 - 051) (Marvel UK) (1986 - 1987)
description:
Spider-Man and Zoids (001 - 051) (Marvel UK) (1986 - 1987)


The first Marvel UK Spider-Man reprint series came to end in December 1985 (with issue 666). After a three month break, Spidey was relaunched with a volume two and a new title - Spider-Man and Zoids. Where he shared the limelight with the Tomy toyline.

51 weekly issues followed, reprinting Marvel US Spider-Man stories and incorporating new strip (featuring the Zoids) from UK creators, including a young Grant Morrison
